testsuite.name: com.typewritermc.protection.flags.FlagEvaluationServiceTest

testcase.name: inherits parent bindings and caches resolved graphs
evaluates bindings by descending region priority
skips incompatible binding types while logging diagnostics
invalidate cascades through the hierarchy and emits update events
